# Installation

Clone repository:

```bash
git clone <repository-url>

Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt
Running the Dashboard

From project directory:

streamlit run app/streamlit.py

The dashboard will open automatically in the browser.

Example Research Results

Example factor comparison:

Portfolio	Annual Return	Sharpe	Maximum Drawdown
Market (SPY)	16.8%	0.74	-33.7%
Momentum	57.4%	1.37	-51.1%
Value	17.9%	0.59	-46.7%
Low Volatility	10.9%	0.55	-32.8%

Interpretation:

Momentum produced the strongest returns but higher downside risk.
Low volatility reduced portfolio risk.
Value performance was more dependent on market regime.
Factor diversification improves portfolio construction flexibility.
